title: War of the Roses: The Chair was Positioned Weird
description: Matt serves in the military and came home to surprise his wife by the local baseball team.  His wife admitted she had cheated on him while he was away but they worked things out. Now there are more things happening to lead Matt to believe she might still be cheating.
